  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5906796">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5906796/" class="title-link">翻译腔十分极其特别生硬</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5906796"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/kuriko./"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u32321640-240.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/kuriko./" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">九月一日才复活</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-04-29"
      class="main-meta">2013-04-29 21:54:45</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5906796_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这个书总体一般，平铺直叙。全是大白话，大白话也就算了。 但是充满了翻译腔。想找到一点中国气息那是别想了。  比如说，皇帝的工作人员。这多么奇怪啊，皇帝的工作人员………………翻译成皇帝的近臣、随侍、有点古意还比工作人员少打两个字呢。  然后就是什么京城出现印刷品…...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5906796/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">12有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5906796_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5906796_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
